        Constructor with the given data, according to positioning type source.
        Parameters:
        longitude - WGS84 Longitude
        latitude - WGS84 Latitude
        used - No. of iBeacons/satellites used
        accuracy - Accuracy (meters)
        found - List including Longitude, Latitude and Accuracy of each iBeacon in the range
        floor - Floor number
        type - Position type: TYPE_NO, TYPE_FUSED, TYPE_GPS or TYPE_NETWORK
        buildingName - Building name if TYPE_IBEACON, null otherwise
        buildingId - Building ID
        geofences - Number of geofences added
